message.body: Hello. Any chance you could bring some of your amazing cookies instead of beans? Someone else told me they were bring beans the other day.
I already started making the beans so I can bring those and also bring cookies.
Scratch that, I'll save the beans for us tomorrow and just bring cookies
Can we borrow your kids picnic table again?
I'll send Jeff over in a bit
It has to be after 12:00. We left for Alex's baseball game so there is no one home
Ok. We'll look for u later. Good luck Alex!
Looks like Alex has a 7:00 tonight so we have to be there by 6:00. Alex & I will only be able to stay until 5:30 but Jim and Grace will stay all evening.
Ok. I'll drink more for you. Wouldn't want you to feel left out. And in sure we'll still be here when you get back
